Categories: FOCUS = keep, polish, promote. KEEP = required & valued. REVIEW = mid-range, judgment call. REQUIRED_INFRA = low V(S) but required for a journey (e.g., /login). CUT_CANDIDATE = low V(S), not required, real cut target. REDUNDANT = duplicates another surface. DEPRECATED = explicit flag. DEAD = no persona uses it.

